OL,3,CMan lost #12,000 after being scammed
OL,4,Cby father and son 'rogue roofers'
OL,6,FA man lost more than #12,000 after
OL,7,Fbeing scammed by father and son "rogue
OL,8,Froofers".
OL,10,FJohn Skipper and his wife Judith, from
OL,11,FCarmarthenshire, were in need of
OL,12,Frepairs to their roof which was badly
OL,13,Fleaking in 2020.
OL,15,FAt the time, John was recovering from
OL,16,Fa stroke and cancer, and was unable to
OL,17,Fcarry out any work himself.
OL,19,FThey were recommended a company, and
OL,20,Fhired builder Jim Janes and his son
OL,21,FThomas Michael Jim James.
