OL,3,CMan lost #12,000 after being scammed
OL,4,Cby father and son 'rogue roofers'
OL,6,FBut they have since been imprisoned
OL,7,Ffor eight years after carrying out
OL,8,Fdozens of faulty roofing repairs
OL,9,Facross south Wales.
OL,11,FIt comes as a new report has found
OL,12,Fmore than #239million has been lost to
OL,13,Frogue builders in Wales over the past
OL,14,Ffive years, with one in 10 Welsh
OL,15,Fhomeowners saying they have suffered
OL,16,Ffinancial loss due to poor or unsafe
OL,17,Fwork. There are calls for a mandatory
OL,18,Flicensing scheme to protect customers
OL,19,Fand the reputation of good builders.
