OL,3,CMan lost #12,000 after being scammed
OL,4,Cby father and son 'rogue roofers'
OL,6,FJohn said he had been reassured that
OL,7,Fthe duo was a legitimate business
OL,8,Fafter visiting their website and
OL,9,Fseeing five-star reviews, alongside a
OL,10,FTrustATrader logo.
OL,12,FAfter being contacted, company owner
OL,13,FJim Janes visited the home and
OL,14,Fprovided a quote of #9,000 for the
OL,15,Fwork.
OL,17,FJohn said this quote was "very
OL,18,Fattractive", saying: "He undercut most
OL,19,Fpeople. It was convincing."
