OL,3,CMan lost #12,000 after being scammed
OL,4,Cby father and son 'rogue roofers'
OL,6,FHowever, things started to change once
OL,7,FJim revised the quote to #12,000 after
OL,8,Ffinding additional problems with the
OL,9,Froof. John says he was disabled at the
OL,10,Ftime and had to accept the extra
OL,11,F#3,000 cost because he couldn't access
OL,12,Fthe roof to verify the added issue.
OL,14,FJohn said: "He turned up with a ragtag
OL,15,Fand bobtail bunch of workers with him.
OL,16,FThey were putting tiles on upside
OL,17,Fdown."
OL,19,FJohn said the condition of the roof
OL,20,Fwas only made worse after the work.
