OL,3,CMan lost #12,000 after being scammed
OL,4,Cby father and son 'rogue roofers'
OL,6,F"It was dry when he was here, but it
OL,7,Frained the following week and the roof
OL,8,Fwas leaking in far more places than
OL,9,Fbefore he arrived," he said. "For the
OL,10,Ffollowing two years, I was chasing him
OL,11,Ffor it to be fixed.
OL,13,F"I was ashamed, I'm the one who will
OL,14,Falways spot someone who will scam you
OL,15,Fa mile off, but here I was scammed.
OL,17,F"He took advantage of me. I told him I
OL,18,Fhad cancer, that I had a stroke, and I
OL,19,Fthink he seemed to delight in that."
