OL,3,CMan lost #12,000 after being scammed
OL,4,Cby father and son 'rogue roofers'
OL,6,FJohn worked with Trading Standards and
OL,7,Ffound out Jim Janes and his son Thomas
OL,8,FMichael Jim James had scammed
OL,9,Fcountless people across south Wales.
OL,11,FIn December 2025, the pair were
OL,12,Fsentenced to eight years in prison for
OL,13,Ftheir part in a roofing scam which
OL,14,Ftargeted 48 homeowners across south
OL,15,Fand west Wales between 2020 and 2025.
OL,17,FTrading standards said the
OL,18,Fprosecutions followed a three year
OL,19,Finvestigation and that the estimated
OL,20,Fdetriment to the 48 homeowners is
OL,21,Fcurrently over #551,000.
