OL,3,CMan lost #12,000 after being scammed
OL,4,Cby father and son 'rogue roofers'
OL,6,FIt was found that the father and son
OL,7,Fcost victims more than #500,000 in
OL,8,Ftotal.
OL,10,FJohn welcomed their conviction,
OL,11,Fsaying: "It was absolute delight and
OL,12,Fthe sentence was absolutely spot on."
OL,14,FThis is not an isolated incident. New
OL,15,Fresearch by the Federation of Master
OL,16,FBuilders (FMB), shared exclusively
OL,17,Fwith ITV Wales, has found that the
OL,18,Ffinancial impact of rogue builders in
OL,19,FWales is estimated to be more than
OL,20,F#239million over the last five years.
