OL,3,CMan lost #12,000 after being scammed
OL,4,Cby father and son 'rogue roofers'
OL,6,FCurrently, anyone can legally operate
OL,7,Fas a builder without needing
OL,8,Fqualifications or experience. FMB's
OL,9,Fresearch found that nearly half of
OL,10,Fhomeowners wrongly believe builders
OL,11,Fneed a licence.
OL,13,FFMB Cymru is calling on the next Welsh
OL,14,FGovernment to work alongside
OL,15,FWestminster colleagues to introduce a
OL,16,Fmandatory licencing scheme for
OL,17,Fbuilding companies. They say this
OL,18,Fmeasure will protect homeowners, as
OL,19,Fwell as the reputation of good
OL,20,Fbuilders.
