OL,6,FThey went on to say: "Unfortunately,
OL,7,Fcompanies and individuals can download
OL,8,Flogos online or create copies of logos
OL,9,Fand use them fraudulently. This is an
OL,10,Fongoing issue not only for
OL,11,FTrustATrader, but also for many
OL,12,Freputable organisations, including
OL,13,FTrading Standards and Gas Safe.
OL,15,F"We would always advise consumers to
OL,16,Fcarry out their own due diligence.
OL,17,FThis includes reading reviews and
OL,18,Fchecking qualifications and insurance
OL,19,Fwhich can be done on the Trustatrader
OL,20,Fwebsite.
